<A>__{adler, looking through binoculars, can't help but smile.}
<C>__{red}
<D>__{gimme' them things.}
<A>__{adler hands over the binoculars. red takes a look. his pov phillip nee casper, walking in his full whitehood, arms reaching for the sky.}
<L>__{exterior field day}
<A>__{phillip reaches level ground and for the first time sees the full strength of the amassed police forces at least}
<L>__{20 cars, swirling lights, guns everywhere, pointing at him. exterior roadside day}
<A>__{red watches.}
<C>__{red}
<P>__{(yells)}
<D>__{come on. keep walkin'!}
<A>__{his pov through binocs phillip stops walking and stands perfectly still.}
<B>__{back to scene}
<A>__{red lowers his binocs.}
